        <Parent_String>barometers [300195808], measuring devices for atmospheric pressure [300198631], meteorological measuring devices [300195712], measuring devices for phenomena [300195703], measuring devices (instruments) [300207870], Measuring Devices (hierarchy name) [300207851], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
